---
---
<section id="solucion" class="mx-auto mt-32 max-w-7xl px-6 sm:mt-56 lg:px-8">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center">
    <h2 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-eco-green">La solucion</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-pretty text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl lg:text-balance">Recoleccion inteligente para ciudades que se anticipan</p>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg/8 text-gray-600">Un sistema que integra datos en tiempo real, inteligencia artificial y optimizacion matematica para que cada camion vaya solo donde se necesita.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-none">
    <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-4">
      <!-- IoT -->
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-gray-900">
          <div class="mb-6 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-eco-green">
            <svg class="size-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.288 15.038a5.25 5.25 0 017.424 0M5.106 11.856c3.807-3.808 9.98-3.808 13.788 0M1.924 8.674c5.565-5.565 14.587-5.565 20.152 0M12.53 18.22l-.53.53-.53-.53a.75.75 0 011.06 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          Monitoreo en tiempo real
        </dt>
        <dd class="mt-1 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base/7 text-gray-600">
          <p class="flex-auto">Sensores IoT en cada contenedor transmiten niveles de ocupacion cada 10 segundos. Sabemos exactamente que contenedores necesitan atencion.</p>
        </dd>
      </div>
      <!-- AI -->
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-gray-900">
          <div class="mb-6 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-eco-green">
            <svg class="size-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904L9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 003.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 003.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09 3.09zM18.259 8.715L18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 002.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 002.455 2.456L21.75 6l-1.036.259a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.455 2.456z"/></svg>
          </div>
          Prediccion con IA
        </dt>
        <dd class="mt-1 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base/7 text-gray-600">
          <p class="flex-auto">Modelos de machine learning predicen que contenedores estaran llenos en las proximas 24 horas, anticipando problemas antes de que ocurran.</p>
        </dd>
      </div>
      <!-- Routes -->
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-gray-900">
          <div class="mb-6 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-eco-green">
            <svg class="size-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 6.75V15m6-6v8.25m.503 3.498l4.875-2.437c.381-.19.622-.58.622-1.006V4.82c0-.836-.88-1.38-1.628-1.006l-3.869 1.934c-.317.159-.69.159-1.006 0L9.503 3.252a1.125 1.125 0 00-1.006 0L3.622 5.689C3.24 5.88 3 6.27 3 6.695V19.18c0 .836.88 1.38 1.628 1.006l3.869-1.934c.317-.159.69-.159 1.006 0l4.994 2.497c.317.158.69.158 1.006 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          Rutas optimizadas
        </dt>
        <dd class="mt-1 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base/7 text-gray-600">
          <p class="flex-auto">Algoritmos de optimizacion combinatoria (TSP + OR-Tools) generan la ruta mas eficiente en menos de 5 segundos, priorizando contenedores criticos.</p>
        </dd>
      </div>
      <!-- NLP -->
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-gray-900">
          <div class="mb-6 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-eco-green">
            <svg class="size-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7.5 8.25h9m-9 3H12m-9.75 1.51c0 1.6 1.123 2.994 2.707 3.227 1.087.16 2.185.283 3.293.369V21l4.076-4.076a1.526 1.526 0 011.037-.443 48.282 48.282 0 005.68-.494c1.584-.233 2.707-1.626 2.707-3.228V6.741c0-1.602-1.123-2.995-2.707-3.228A48.394 48.394 0 0012 3c-2.392 0-4.744.175-7.043.513C3.373 3.746 2.25 5.14 2.25 6.741v6.018z"/></svg>
          </div>
          Lenguaje natural
        </dt>
        <dd class="mt-1 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base/7 text-gray-600">
          <p class="flex-auto">IBM Watsonx convierte datos tecnicos en instrucciones claras para conductores, reportes para gestores y alertas para ciudadanos.</p>
        </dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>
</section>
